//! 1. `Part::scope()` matches the spec's `data-ars-scope` token.
//! 2. `Part::all()` produces exactly the declared parts in the declared
//!    order.
//! 3. Every declared part round-trips through `Part::name()` with the
//!    declared kebab-case token.
